arts.ttl: Udinese vs. Atalanta, opens Matchday ten
arts.sum: The tenth matchday of Serie A begins at the Blunergy Stadium with Udinese facing Atalanta. Atalanta are the only unbeaten team after nine matchdays in Serie A 2025/26, as was also the case in 2022/23.
Serie A is providing intriguing narratives at the top and bottom of the table and Elliott Bretland has correct-score picks for all ten Serie A matches this weekend.
